CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season - Sitting One Out - What is a formal without a pretty girl? Here Mrs. Ruby Jackson of East Pittsburgh sits one out at the Frogs' formal. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Ruby Jackson wearing strapless light colored gown with multiple ruffles, seated on sofa in Gateway Plaza for FROGS formal
